::Spears::

She heard him say something about 'wouldn't be a long way'.  She 
smiled.  SHe knew he was starting to like her. But she was starting 
to lik him too.  She stopped, stood still,turned and looked at him. 
She smiled at him with a warm smile.
"If you insist, I am in no shape to put up a fight right now."
She chuckled slightly.
